data.description:
Looking for a beautiful 3-bedroom home on a larger lot featuring 2 spacious living rooms, 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with a bonus room all perfectly situated in a quiet neighborhood on almost a half-acre! The large, fenced backyard has a large wood deck perfect for outdoor entertaining. Conveniently located in the Forest Woods Subdivision close to everything from shopping, restaurants, Ft. Liberty/Bragg, and all without an HOA or City Taxes! ***Seller is offering a $10,000 Buyer incentive to be used towards closing costs or to buy down buyer rate!*** Call today to schedule a showing!!
Home appraised at $295,000.
